ito]], [[Recife/Guararapes\u2013Gilberto Freyre International Airport|Recife]], [[Leonardo da Vinci\u2013Fiumicino Airport|Rome\u2013Fiumicino]], [[Deputado Lu\u00eds Eduardo Magalh\u00e3es International Airport|Salvador da Bahia]], [[Ram\u00f3n Villeda Morales International Airport|San Pedro Sula]], [[Viru Viru International Airport|Santa Cruz de la Sierra\u2013Viru Viru]], [[Las Am\u00e9ricas International Airport|Santo Domingo\u2013Las Americas]], [[S\u00e3o Paulo\u2013Guarulhos International Airport|S\u00e3o Paulo\u2013Guarulhos]], [[Seville Airport|Seville]], [[Ben Gurion Airport|Tel Aviv]], [[Tenerife North Airport|Tenerife\u2013North]], [[Tunis-Carthage International Airport|Tunis]], [[Valencia Airport|Valencia]], [[Venice Marco Polo Airport|Venice]], [[Vigo-Peinador Airport|Vigo]], [[Z\u00fcrich Airport|Z\u00fcrich]] <br> '''Seasonal:''' [[Alghero\u2013Fertilia Airport|Alghero]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Air Europa adds seasonal Alghero service in S19 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/283820/air-europa-adds-seasonal-alghero-service-in-s19/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=10 April 2019}}</ref> [[Athens International Airport|Athens]], [[Copenhagen Airport|Copenhagen]], [[Santorini (Thira) International Airport|Santorini]] (begins 3 July 2020),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/287404/air-europa-adds-madrid-thira-service-in-s20/|title=Air Europa adds Madrid \u2013 Thira service in S20|first=Jim|last=Liu|publisher=routesonline.com|date=7 November 2019}}</ref> [[Stockholm Arlanda Airport|Stockholm\u2013Arlanda]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Air France]] | [[Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]], [[Orly Airport|Paris\u2013Orly]]<ref name=\"Destinations JOON\">[https://www.airfrance.fr/FR/fr/local/home/joon/ProductAndServicesJoonAction.do?page=destinations MADRID 1ers vols \u00e0 compter du 31 mars 2019] Air France. 26 October 2018.</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Air France resumes Paris Orly \u2013 Madrid service in S20 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/287225/air-france-resumes-paris-orly-madrid-service-in-s20/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=30 October 2019}}</ref> \n<!-- -->\n|[[Air India]] | [[Indira Gandhi International Airport|Delhi]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Air Moldova]] | [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u International Airport|Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Air Serbia]] | [[Belgrade Airport|Belgrade]] \n<!-- -->\n|[[Air Transat]] |[[Montr\u00e9al-Pierre Elliott Trudeau International Airport|Montr\u00e9al\u2013Trudeau]]<ref>https://www.lelezard.com/communique-18795106.html</ref>\n<!-- -->\n|[[Alitalia]] | [[Linate Airport|Milan\u2013Linate]], [[Leonardo da Vinci\u2013Fiumicino Airport|Rome\u2013Fiumicino]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[American Airlines]] | [[Dallas/Fort Worth International Airport|Dallas/Fort Worth]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[John F. Kennedy International Airport|New York\u2013JFK]], [[Philadelphia International Airport|Philadelphia]]<br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Charlotte/Douglas International Airport|Charlotte]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Avianca]] | [[El Dorado International Airport|Bogot\u00e1]], [[Alfonso Bonilla Arag\u00f3n International Airport|Cali]], [[Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda C\u00f3rdova International Airport|Medell\u00edn\u2013JMC]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Beijing Capital Airlines]] | [[Chengdu Shuangliu International Airport|Chengdu]], [[Hangzhou Xiaoshan International Airport|Hangzhou]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Blue Air]] |[[Henri Coand\u0103 International Airport|Bucharest]]<br>'''Seasonal:''' [[George Enescu International Airport|Bac\u0103u]]{{fact|date=April 2020}}\n<!-- -->\n|[[Boliviana de Aviaci\u00f3n]] | [[Jorge Wilstermann International Airport|Cochabamba]], [[Viru Viru International Airport|Santa Cruz de la Sierra\u2013Viru Viru]] \n<!-- -->\n|[[British Airways]] | [[Heathrow Airport|London\u2013Heathrow]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Brussels Airlines]] | [[Brussels Airport|Brussels]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Bulgaria Air]] | [[Sofia Airport|