eria.es/news/13112019/estrenamos-vuelos-directos-a-washington</ref> [[Zagreb Airport|Zagreb]], [[Zurich Airport|Z\u00fcrich]] <br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Bastia \u2013 Poretta Airport|Bastia]],<ref name=\"Liu, Jim\">{{cite web |url= https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/283064/iberia-further-expands-european-routes-in-s19/ |title= Iberia further expands European routes in S19 |language= English |publisher= Routesonline.com |date= 21 February 2019 |author= Liu, Jim |accessdate= 21 February 2018}}</ref> [[Bergen Airport|Bergen]], [[Cairo International Airport|Cairo]], [[Catania-Fontanarossa Airport|Catania]], [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]],<ref name=\"Liu, Jim\">{{cite web |url= https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/283064/iberia-further-expands-european-routes-in-s19/ |title= Iberia further expands European routes in S19 |language= English |publisher= Routesonline.com |date= 21 February 2019 |author= Liu, Jim |accessdate= 21 February 2018}}</ref> [[Dubrovnik Airport|Dubrovnik]], [[Faro Airport|Faro]], [[F\u00e8s\u2013Sa\u00efs Airport|Fez]] (begins 28 July 2020),<ref name=\"fes\">{{cite web |url= https://grupo.iberia.es/news/11122019/fez-y-liubliana-los-nuevos-destinos-de-iberia-para-el-verano-de-2020 |title= Fez y Liubliana, los nuevos destinos de Iberia para el verano de 2020 |language= Spanish |publisher= Iberia |accessdate= 15 December 2019}}</ref> [[Genoa Cristoforo Colombo Airport|Genoa]], [[Gran Canaria Airport|Gran Canaria]], [[Ljubljana Jo\u017ee Pu\u010dnik Airport|Ljubljana]] (begins 28 July 2020),<ref name=\"fes\"/> [[Moscow\u2013Domodedovo]], [[Olbia \u2013 Costa Smeralda Airport|Olbia]], [[Pulkovo Airport|Saint Petersburg]], [[San Francisco International Airport|San Francisco]], [[Split Airport|Split]] <br> '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Al Maktoum International Airport|Dubai\u2013Al Maktoum]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Liu|first1=Jim|title=Iberia schedules Dubai al Maktoum charters in late-Dec 2019|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/