ital]], [[Mohammed V International Airport|Casablanca]], [[Copenhagen Airport|Copenhagen]], [[East Midlands Airport|East Midlands]], [[Frankfurt International Airport|Frankfurt]], [[Leipzig/Halle Airport|Leipzig/Halle]], [[London\u2013Heathrow]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Milan\u2013Malpensa]], [[Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Emirates Sky Cargo]] | [[Al Maktoum International Airport|Dubai\u2013Al Maktoum]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[FedEx Feeder]] | [[Dublin Airport|Dublin]], [[Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Kalitta Air]] | [[Miami International Airport|Miami]] \n<!-- -->\n|[[MASkargo]] | [[Frankfurt Airport|Frankfurt]], [[Kuala Lumpur International Airport|Kuala Lumpur\u2013International]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Qatar Airways Cargo]]| [[Hamad International Airport|Doha]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Swiftair]] | [[Houari Boumediene Airport|Algiers]], [[Athens International Airport|Athens]], [[Barcelona Airport|Barcelona]], [[bilbao Airport|Bilbao]], [[Mohammed V International Airport|Casablanca]], [[Gran Canaria Airport|Gran Canaria]], [[Larnaca International Airport|Larnaca]], [[Lisbon Airport|Lisbon]], [[Milan Malpensa Airport|Milan\u2013Malpensa]], [[Mallorca Airport|Palma de Mallorca]], [[Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]], [[Stockholm Arlanda Airport|Stockholm\u2013Arlanda]], [[Tenerife North Airport|Tenerife\u2013North]]<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.swiftair.com/servicios_en/rutas.html| title=Routes| publisher=Swiftair| accessdate=30 June 2017| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423142910/http://www.swiftair.com/servicios_en/rutas.html| archive-date=23 April 2015| url-status=dead| df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n|{{nowrap|[[Turkish Cargo]]}} | [[Houari Boumediene Airport|Algiers]], [[Belgrade Nikola Tesla Airport|Belgrade]], [[Mohammed V International Airport|Casablanca]], [[George Bush Intercontinental Airport|Houston-Intercontinental]], [[Atat\u00fcrk International A